Insider Activity


Individual




John K. Wulff



Mr. John K. Wulff is on the Board of Directors at Atlas Air Worldwide Holdings, Inc., Chemtura Corp. and Celanese Corp. Mr. Wulff was previously employed as an Independent Director by Moody's Corp., an Independent Director by Sunoco, Inc., Non-Executive Chairman by Hercules, Inc., a Member by Financial Accounting Standards Board, Chief Financial Officer by Union Carbide Corp., and Partner by KPMG LLP. He also served on the board at Federal National Mortgage Association. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Pennsylvania.



