(March 4th, 2005)
This Directors Deferred Compensation and Benefits Trust Agreement, Amended and Restated effective as of December 23, 2002, (the Trust Agreement), is by and among SUNOCO, INC., a Pennsylvania corporation (the Company), MELLON TRUST OF NEW ENGLAND, N.A., a national association (the Trustee), and TOWERS PERRIN, FORSTER & CROSBY, INC., a Pennsylvania corporation (the Recordkeeper).




FANNIE MAE RESTRICTED STOCK AWARD FOR NONMANAGEMENT DIRECTORS Award Document
(December 9th, 2004)
This grant of Restricted Stock from Fannie Mae (the Award) is made to you as a Nonmanagement Director (the Awardee) effective as of the date of grant set forth in Exhibit A attached hereto.




Schedule to the Form of the Amended and Restated Indemnification Agreement
(May 7th, 2004)
The Amended and Restated Indemnification Agreements between Sunoco, Inc. and the directors, executive officers, trustees, fiduciaries, employees or agents named below are identical in all material respects.





